OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F127 fuel drivers apply for 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FUK visa                    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%title3
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Only 127 fuel drivers from overseas    
OL,6, have applied for temporary visas aimed 
OL,7, at tackling shortages, the prime       
OL,8, minister has said.                     
OL,10,FThe government is offering immediate   
OL,11,Fvisas for 300 foreign tanker drivers to
OL,12,Fwork in the UK from now until the end  
OL,13,Fof March to deliver fuel to forecourts.
OL,15,FMr Johnson said it was a "fascinating  
OL,16,Fillustration of the problem", which he 
OL,17,Fadded was a "global" issue.            
OL,19,FHowever, he said there was a           
OL,20,F"particular problem in the UK".        
